[Water]
Original Mint Collection
For 06/2022

3840 x 3840 Pix, 300DPI
PNG

The light leaking from outside lights the bathroom with a subtle silver color.
Riding the sweet scent in the ice sugar of the magic tea spoon,
The magic water cools the hot blood that flows through her body.

Your attention has created this painting. Thank you.
